Package: pplmatch
Title: Match Parliamentary Debate Speakers to Member Records
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for matching parliamentary debate speakers to official member records
    using fuzzy matching techniques. Supports both Canadian Parliament (fuzzyjoin) and
    Quebec National Assembly (multi-level deterministic + fuzzy via Python/rapidfuzz).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    fuzzyjoin,
    tidyr,
    reticulate,
    tibble,
    purrr,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
